# Design System — Maxima

> Extracted from [https://maximatherapy.com/](https://maximatherapy.com/)
> Generated by Ditto on April 9, 2026

## 1. Visual Theme & Atmosphere

The design follows a **dark theme** with a rich, dark background (`#000000`). The primary accent color is a **orange** (`#fd4401`) used for interactive elements and brand moments.

Typography is built on **ui-sans-serif** for headings and **ABC Diatype Rounded Plus** for body text, creating a balanced dual-family system.

**Key Characteristics:**
- Dark background (`#000000`) with light text (`#ffffff`)
- Primary accent: `#fd4401`
- Font: ui-sans-serif (headings) / ABC Diatype Rounded Plus (body)
- Border radius: 4.7619px – 14.2857px
- Heading weight: 400, Body weight: 500

## 2. Color Palette & Roles

### Primary
- **Orange** (`#fd4401`): Primary brand color, CTAs, interactive highlights — 36 occurrences

### Secondary
- **Dark Blue** (`#2668fd`): Secondary accent, supporting elements

### Accent
- **Yellow** (`#fdcb40`): Accent color, decorative elements

### Background
- **Black** (`#000000`): Page background — 336 occurrences

### Text Primary
- **White** (`#ffffff`): Primary heading and body text — 28 occurrences


