- **Heading**: ui-sans-serif, fallback: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif
- **Body**: ABC Diatype Rounded Plus, fallback: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif
- **Monospace**: ui-monospace, fallback: ui-monospace, monospace

