- "Design a card: `#f8fafc` background, 1px solid `#e2e8f0`, 14.2857px radius. Shadow: `0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`. Title at 1.25rem weight 400, `#ffffff`. Body at 19.0476px weight 500, `#475569`."

### Iteration Guide
1. Always use the defined color palette — no ad-hoc colors
2. Heading weight is 400, body weight is 500
3. Border radius: 4.7619px (small), 4.7619px (default), 14.2857px (large)
4. Use the spacing scale: xs(4.19047px), sm(6.66666px), md(13.3333px), lg(26.6666px), xl(26.6666px)
5. Shadow levels: sm, md, lg — use consistently
